snippet.title: Merchants of Rosewall - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Manage your shop by hiring giants, elves, orcs, and more from different walks of life. Lose yourself in the rich narrative of a fantasy world like no other, and maybe even unravel a mystery of the past. What will you create in Merchants of Rosewall?

Wishlist our game! https://bit.ly/49Yd0gX 
Join our Discord server! https://discord.gg/99FwFMjqY5
Find us on social media! https://linktr.ee/bigblueskygames

Trailer credit: https://www.indiebard.co/
Music credit: https://www.fatbard.com/
